oselia에 전부를 걸었다」잖아!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"episode090-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"앗. 이런 곳에까지 자수가 새겨져 있어!\n난 이런 거 할 줄 모르는데!!\n린코, 바느질은 어디서 배운 거야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"episode090-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"인터넷으로…… 전부 독학이라서……\n이, 이상할…… 지도요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"odoodo02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"episode090-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"뭐어~!? 이거 학원 다닌 거 아니었어?\n천재잖아……! 우와~~~ 굉장하네! 진짜!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","tim