alkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"그, 그렇지 않아요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"episode090-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"하지만 날티 나는 애가 손으로 인형을 뜬다니?\n뭔가 이상하잖아~\n그래서 별로 다른 사람에겐 얘기 안 해.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"episode090-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"……말할 수 없는 그 마음…… 이해해요.\n저도…… 설마, 제가 직접 지은 옷을\n누군가가…… 입어준……다니……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"episode090-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"저…… 생각했던 것보다 훨씬…… 기뻐요……\n이마이 씨…… 즐거워해 주셔서……\n저 혼자…… 즐겼던 때보다…… 훨씬 더……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"